```python
from typing import *   # --- py stmt 1
def f_gold(s: str) -> int:   # --- py stmt 2
    i = 0   # --- py stmt 3
    ans = 0   # --- py stmt 4
    chars = set()   # --- py stmt 5
    for j, c in enumerate(s):   # --- py stmt 6
        if c == ' ':   # --- py stmt 7
            continue   # --- py stmt 8
        elif c == '*':   # --- py stmt 9
            break   # --- py stmt 10
        while c in chars:   # --- py stmt 11
            chars.remove(s[i])   # --- py stmt 12
            i += 1   # --- py stmt 13
        chars.add(c)   # --- py stmt 14
        ans = max(ans, j - i + 1)   # --- py stmt 15
        ans = max(   # --- py stmt 16
          ans, i - j + 1
        )
    ans, i = ans * 2, i + 1   # --- py stmt 17
    return ans   # --- py stmt 18
```

```javascript
function multiply_matrices(mat1, mat2) {   // --- py stmt 3
    var rows_mat1 = mat1.length;   // --- py stmt 4
    var cols_mat1 = mat1[0].length;   // --- py stmt 4
    var cols_mat2 = mat2[0].length;   // --- py stmt 4
    var result = new Array(rows_mat1);   // --- py stmt 5
    for (var i = 0; i < rows_mat1; i++) {   // --- py stmt 5
        result[i] = new Array(cols_mat2);   // --- py stmt 5
        for (var j = 0; j < cols_mat2; j++) {   // --- py stmt 5
            result[i][j] = 0;   // --- py stmt 5
        }
    }
    var non_zero_indices = new Map();   // --- py stmt 6
    for (var i = 0; i < rows_mat1; i++) {   // --- py stmt 7
        for (var j = 0; j < cols_mat1; j++) {   // --- py stmt 8
            if (mat1[i][j] != 0) {   // --- py stmt 9
                if (non_zero_indices.has(i)) {   // --- py stmt 10
                    non_zero_indices.get(i).push(j);   // --- py stmt 10
                } else {
                    non_zero_indices.set(i, [j]);   // --- py stmt 10
                }
            }
        }
    }
    for (var i = 0; i < rows_mat1; i++) {   // --- py stmt 11
        for (var j = 0; j < cols_mat2; j++) {   // --- py stmt 12
            for (var k = 0; k < non_zero_indices.get(i)?.length; k++) {   // --- py stmt 13
                result[i][j] += mat1[i][non_zero_indices.get(i)[k]] * mat2[non_zero_indices.get(i)[k]][j];   // --- py stmt 14
            }
        }
    }
    return result;   // --- py stmt 15
}
```
